{"tid":1156186,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【保安局覆立會法律顧問】保安局：單次移交不可行 不排除當年立法較匆忙","createTime":"2019-05-15T12:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T12:32:19.000Z","uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"37f6014a9b5f1efb8d2b9f65f8783d857189cddb","tid":1156186,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T12:32:19.000Z","msg":"立場報道2019/5/15 &mdash; 19:04<br />\n<br />\n【覆立會法律顧問】被質疑現有單次移交為何不可行 保安局：不排除當年立法較匆忙<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/tso-19_1zwKr_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftso-19_1zwKr_1200x0.png&h=e82ebcbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會法律顧問曹志遠早前去信保安局，就人權保障等25項範疇提出 25 項質疑要求澄清，保安局昨日（14日）發出長達 18 頁的信件回覆曹志遠，指《逃犯條例》不適用於香港特區與中國其他部分之間的移交，並非刻意剔除。對於曹志遠問及，為何政府指現有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">單次移交安排不切實可行，保安局指當年立法會二讀階段，涉及單次移交安排討論亦甚少，不排除這安排是「較匆忙的建議」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n曹志遠指出，回歸前立法局討論《逃犯條例》時，剔除移交逃犯至中國其他部分是政策原意，政府有意另行與內地訂立正式引渡安排，保安局回覆稱並非刻意剔除。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保安局解釋，《逃犯條例》旨在把港英年代沿用的引渡法例作本地化立法，「《逃犯條例》不適用於香港特區與中國任何其他部分之間的移交逃犯安排，反映當時被本地化的安排不包括中華人民共和國在內，而不是將中國任何其他部分在法例本地化時刻意剔除」。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A6%86%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F-%E8%A2%AB%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E7%8F%BE%E6%9C%89%E5%96%AE%E6%AC%A1%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C-%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80-%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E8%BC%83%E5%8C%86%E5%BF%99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A6%2586%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%2599%25A4%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25BC%2583%25E5%258C%2586%25E5%25BF%2599%2F&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2K2paxXJRTFpYESBXKIXFX0%3D&h=b53f55bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25A6%2586%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2596%25AE%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25BD%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%2599%25A4%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25BC%2583%25E5%258C%2586%25E5%25BF%2599%2F&h=1c75abf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%A6%86%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F-%E8%A2%AB%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E7%8F%BE%E6%9C%89%E5%96%AE%E6%AC%A1%E7%A7%BB%E4%BA%A4%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%A1%8C-%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80-%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E8%BC%83%E5%8C%86%E5%BF%99/</a>"}]}